## 运行

docker-compose up -d

## load_tpch_to_hive
从指定目录导入数据到hive中

## hadoop-conf hadoop-home hadoop-native
配置hive

## 下载preso-jar
  $ wget https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/io/prestosql/presto-cli/308/presto-cli-308-executable.jar
  $ mv presto-cli-308-executable.jar presto.jar
  $ chmod +x presto.jar

## start.sh 
  连接presto,执行命令